  "summary": {
    "en": "A compact fort-and-tent building set for younger builders, combining glow play, simple assembly, and gift-ready packaging.",
    "zh": "适合低龄儿童的堡垒帐篷拼搭套装，兼具发光玩法、简易组装和礼品化包装。"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": [
      "The 69-piece configuration is suitable for small forts, tent frames, reading corners, and lightweight indoor exploration spaces.",
      "PP rods and rounded connector balls support repeated assembly while keeping the structure easy for children to handle.",
      "Glow-style play adds stronger gift appeal for bedrooms, family activities, and seasonal promotions.",
      "The color box, storage bag, and instruction sheet make the set practical for retail, e-commerce, and OEM/ODM programs."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "69件配置适合搭建小型堡垒、帐篷框架、阅读角和轻量室内探索空间。",
      "PP杆件与圆润连接球支持反复拆装，结构轻便，儿童更容易操作。",
      "发光玩法增强卧室场景、亲子活动和节庆礼品渠道的吸引力。",
      "彩盒、收纳袋和说明书配置完整，适合零售、电商和OEM/ODM项目。"
    ]
  },
